diary_entry: Through the morning until the afternoon paine was pretty good then I had a gig well one of the members was a bit late so we were really frantic to get onstage so ended up moving a bit of stuff and I also played tambourine and bruised my hand a little bit so I was a bit sore by the time I finish playing.
